&lt;p&gt;The Data for AI team is a small, specialized group within Similarweb, working closely with a select set of the world’s leading AI organizations (mostly foundational model companies). The team’s mission is to enable these companies to improve their models and AI assistants by applying Similarweb’s data to real-world AI use cases.&lt;/p&gt;
