&lt;p data-start=&quot;2846&quot; data-end=&quot;2964&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an experienced and impact driven professional to join our global Risk team as a Senior Deal Strategist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2966&quot; data-end=&quot;3250&quot;&gt;In this role, you will take a leading part in shaping risk and commercial decision making across APAC and EMEA. You will work closely with go to market leadership, bringing strong analytical judgment, business understanding, and a forward looking perspective to complex opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3252&quot; data-end=&quot;3505&quot;&gt;This role is designed for someone who already has solid experience operating in analytical and commercial environments and is ready to take broader ownership, influence strategy, and act as a trusted partner to Sales, Finance, and regional stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3512&quot; data-end=&quot;3536&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3512&quot; data-end=&quot;3536&quot;&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3538&quot; data-end=&quot;4406&quot;&gt;Own and lead regional risk and analytics initiatives, including exposure analysis, KPI definition, ROI modeling, and value articulation for key merchants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3538&quo

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Forter seeks a highly skilled, motivated Senior Full-Stack Engineer&amp;nbsp; to join the Customer Experience Offerings (CXO) team. This team delivers and scales Forter’s core offerings and agentic experiences, creating smart automation for customers to confidently understand, configure, and optimize their journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Part of the Customer Experience group, this high-impact, hands-on role involves working across the full application stack—frontend (React, Next.js), backend (Node.js, TypeScript), data pipelines, and platform development. The ideal candidate has deep expertise in full-stack development, large-scale data stores, event-driven pipelines, data models, and high-throughput infrastructure. You will design and implement robust, end-to-end solutions for the customer portal and internal tools, and play a central role in shaping AI-driven capabilities as we invest heavily in Agentic AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy owning complex problems end to end, improving systems at scale, and building experiences that bring real value to customers, we would love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the end-to-end technical strategy and development for Forter&#39;s core offerings and the intelligent, agentic experiences that empower customers to configure and continuously optimize their journey.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and implemen

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Forter’s CX group owns the &quot;face&quot; of our products. In this role, your mission is twofold: you will define the innovative experience patterns and &quot;agentic&quot; flows that set the standard for all Forter products, while also taking full ownership of major, standalone strategic projects. You will lead the evolution of our platform into the agentic era, reimagining how users interact with AI-driven workflows to meet shifting market expectations. Bridging the gap between high-level strategy and technical execution, you will ensure every touchpoint in the ecosystem is seamless and value-driven. You’ll partner closely with Design and Engineering to raise our UX quality bar and embed practical AI into the fabric of the merchant experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Strategic Standalone Projects:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full end-to-end ownership of major product initiatives. You will move from initial market discovery and strategy to technical execution and global launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define the &quot;Forter Experience&quot; Standards:&lt;/strong&gt; Create and document the innovative experience patterns and &quot;agentic&quot; flows that define how merchants interact with our platform. You’ll ensure these patterns are modular and high-quality so other PMs can easil

