&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Forter is looking for a &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Software AI Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;to join a strong and dynamic AI Engineering team&lt;/em&gt;. We are the focal point for AI initiatives in Forter, striving to constantly bring innovation and leverage AI capabilities across all company teams and products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
