&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a hands-on, data-driven &lt;strong&gt;Paid Social User Acquisition Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to join our Growth Team. Reporting directly to a Growth Team Lead, you&#39;ll own paid social and display acquisition across Meta, TikTok&amp;nbsp; and additional channels - with a clear mandate to expand these channels across multiple AutoDS group brands and scale them profitably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a builder&#39;s role. You&#39;ll be the person who takes a channel from zero to ROAS-positive - then scales it aggressively across brands. You&#39;ll be in the accounts every day, but you&#39;ll also be thinking about how to systematize what works and replicate it across the portfolio. If you&#39;ve scaled paid acquisition across multiple brands or product lines while keeping ROAS he

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;AutoDS&lt;/strong&gt;, recently acquired by Fiverr, we&#39;re revolutionizing the eCommerce world by providing innovative tools that empower online sellers globally. As a fast-growing company, we’re looking for talented individuals who are passionate about technology, eCommerce, and making a real impact. If you&#39;re ready to join a dynamic team and thrive in a collaborative, fast-paced environment, we’d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior User Acquisition Manager - Google Ads&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
