&lt;p&gt;A hardworking, product-driven person who takes real ownership and is passionate about product and problem-solving. You should be able to independently analyze large-scale datasets (B2C) and turn insights into clear decisions, with a flexible mindset and the ability to think big.&lt;/p&gt;
