&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Visual Generative AI Solutions Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our AI Lab — a cross-functional group driving innovation, experimentation, and advanced AI capabilities across Lightricks. We&#39;re looking for someone who lives in the visual generation space — diffusion models, video synthesis, and the creative pipelines that bring them to life in production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the intersection of &lt;strong&gt;applied AI, creative technology, and product&lt;/strong&gt;. You’ll work hands-on with &lt;strong&gt;LTX-2 workflows and open-source generative models&lt;/strong&gt;, prototype new capabilities, help bring AI solutions to market, and act as a domain expert supporting teams across the company — from Product and Design to Sales and Business Development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role requires &lt;strong&gt;technical depth in generative AI&lt;/strong&gt;, strong ownership, curiosity, and a passion for pushing creative AI forward.&lt;/p&gt;
